THE MARKET · node MKT · MKT · THE MARKET · agora · where prices are found · UD0 / agora

universe of origin : a sphere of the marketplace
seal               : No one sets the price of bread. It emerges — from millions of buyers wanting more when it's cheap and sellers offering more when it's dear, meeting at a number that clears the shelves. The market is a vast, leaderless computer for discovering what things are worth, and a vast, leaderless way for that discovery to go wrong.
